Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.10,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}saita no wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.28,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}soko ni tane ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.28,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ochita kara de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:57.91,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Itsuka mata kareta ato de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:05.13,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}tane ni natte sidzuiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:14.09,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kouya o kakeru, kono ryouashi de (going going) sore dake nanda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:21.68,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Asu e tabidatsu jumbi wa ii kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.44,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Soko de tomadou, demo unmei ga (calling calling) yondeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.65,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}naraba subete o ikitte yare
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:39.16,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Nankai datte yuu yo, sekai wa utsukushii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:47.59,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}kimi ga sore o akiramenai kara dayo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:54.80,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Saishuukai no story wa hajime kara kimateita to shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:02:02.06,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ima dake wa koko ni aru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:06.69,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}kimi no mama hikatte yuke yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sesuatu yang mekar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}dari bunga itu adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}sebuah biji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yang jatuh ke tanah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:57.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Suatu saat nanti, tanaman yang kering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:05.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}meninggalkan biji dan menjadi keturunan baru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:14.09,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kulalui tanah gersang dengan kedua kakiku ini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:21.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Apa kau sudah siap untuk perjalanan besok pagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sedikit rasa ragu, namun takdir seolah memanggilku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Maka hiduplah dengan apa yang kaupunya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:39.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Kuulangi berulang kali, dunia ini memanglah indah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:47.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}karena dirimu tidak menyerah padanya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:54.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Meski kisahku telah ditetapkan sejak awal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:02:02.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}tapi aku masih di sini, detik ini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:06.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Maka bersinarlah seperti yang kaumau
